_sText:
Note:
This map is created for Gun Reloading Zombie Mod and also CSS Deathmatch.  This is not a barricade type of zombie map, it is made to be realistic with high detail.  My goal was to create a realistic zombie lake map since all the other I've seen are poorly made.

Details:
The map is centered around a large lake in the middle with houses on either side.  There is also a sewer system that connects the two houses with plenty of quick exits.  The map has great creepy characteristics great for zombie invasions.

Final:
I do plan on creating more versions of this map to include better optimization, soundscapes, and different game type compatibilities.  Also I am working on creating a Hondo inspired version, if you know what I mean.

This is my first published map and I would greatly appreciate input.
My email is: rapidcore85@gmail.com
My Steam Name is: enano_salvaje

Thank you for downloading my map!

enano_salvaje
